    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still turns heads? This car has been my absolute favorite for weekend trips and daily commutes alike! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road with a new owner immediately. It drives super smoothly and is just waiting for its next adventure. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
