      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2). This 3.6L flat-six powerhouse features a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal. The 6-speed manual transaxle delivers precise engagement, complemented by a factory-optioned limited-slip differential. Chassis dynamics are enhanced by Bilstein B6 dampers and refreshed bushings, ensuring neutral handling and high-speed stability. Braking performance is sharp, utilizing four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors. While the exterior shows honest road patina, the mechanicals are synchronized for peak performance. A turn-key analog sports car for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
