    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that offers a superb blend of performance and everyday utility. The exterior maintains a high-gloss finish, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch near the driver-side door handle\u2014honest signs of careful use. The alloy wheels are in excellent shape with no significant curb rash. Inside, the interior remains remarkably fresh; the seats are firm and free of tears, and the dashboard is pristine with no sun fading or cracks. All electronic features, including the dual-zone climate control and the premium audio system, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs quietly, reflecting a history of timely oil changes and proactive maintenance. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brake pads were recently replaced. This car drives straight and true, offering a smooth ride that feels solid on the road. It is a reliable, well-documented vehicle ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 32500.0,
